'''珊曼莎·弗羅倫斯·「珊」·貝莉'''（{{lang-en|Samantha Florence "Sam" Bailey}}，{{bd|1977年|6月29日}}）英國歌手，以贏得2013年{{引书号转换|{{lang|en|[[英國版X音素|X音素]]}}}}（{{lang|en|''The X Factor''}}）第十季的比賽而廣為人知。

==早年生活==
貝莉出生在[[倫敦|倫敦]]Bexley，父母分別是羅尼（{{lang|en|Ronnie}}，1950{{ndash}}2008）<ref name="brothers">{{cite news|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/x-factor-sam-bailey-saved-2928359|title=X Factor Sam Bailey saved her boozy brother's life after both were left heartboken by father's death|last=Brankin|first=Emma|date=2013-12-15|work=[[Daily_Mirror|Daily Mirror]]|publisher=[[Trinity_Mirror|Trinity Mirror]]|accessdate=2014-06-24|archive-date=2014-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217153615/http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/x-factor-sam-bailey-saved-2928359|dead-url=no}}</ref>和賈姬·貝莉（{{lang|en|Jackie Bailey}}）。<ref name="Jackie Bailey">{{cite news|url=http://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/X-Factor-house-Meet-Sam-Bailey-s-number-fans-home/story-19992453-detail/story.html|title=X Factor house: Meet Sam Bailey's number one fans - back home in Leicester|date=2013-10-25|work=[[Leicester_Mercury|Leicester Mercury]]|publisher=[[Local_World|Local World]]|accessdate=2014-06-24|archive-date=2014-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020005631/http://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/X-Factor-house-Meet-Sam-Bailey-s-number-fans-home/story-19992453-detail/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她有兩個兄弟，查理（{{lang|en|Charlie}}）和丹尼（{{lang|en|Danny}}）。<ref name="brothers"/>羅尼在2008年因[[口腔癌|口腔癌]]而逝世。<ref name="brothers"/>

==音樂事業==
===早期事業===
1996年，18歲的貝莉和好友茱莉·納尼（{{lang|en|Julie Nunney}}）組成雙人團體{{lang|en|Girls Next Door}}，灌錄[[斯卡曲風|斯卡]]風格的〈{{lang|en|Too Late}}〉，由{{lang|en|Right Said Fred}}的貝斯手克萊德·華德（{{lang|en|Clyde Ward}}）製作。

==個人生活==
貝莉現在與丈夫克雷格·皮爾森（{{lang|en|Craig Pearson}}）<ref name="express"/>和三個孩子湯米（{{lang|en|Tommy}}）、布魯克（{{lang|en|Brooke}}）和麥莉（{{lang|en|Miley}}）<ref name="xfactor2">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2449042/Prison-officer-Sam-Screwbo-Bailey-leads-pampered-parade-X-Factor-finalists-superstar-makeovers.html|title=What a transformation! Prison officer Sam 'Screwbo' Bailey leads the pampered parade as the X Factor finalists get superstar makeovers|date=7 October 2013|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|publisher=[[DMG_Media|DMG Media]]|accessdate=8 October 2013|archive-date=2013-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131008202034/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2449042/Prison-officer-Sam-Screwbo-Bailey-leads-pampered-parade-X-Factor-finalists-superstar-makeovers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[史賓格犬|史賓格犬]]茉莉（{{lang|en|Molly}}）<ref name="express">{{cite web|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/448303/X-Factor-finalist-Sam-Bailey-heads-home-to-Leicester-to-greet-her-husband-and-children|title=X Factor finalist Sam Bailey heads home to Leicester to greet her husband and children|date=12 December 2013|last=McCormack|first=Kirsty|work=[[Daily_Express|Daily Express]]|accessdate=15 December 2013|archive-date=2014-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205033550/http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/448303/X-Factor-finalist-Sam-Bailey-heads-home-to-Leicester-to-greet-her-husband-and-children|dead-url=no}}</ref> 住在[[萊斯特|萊斯特]]。<ref name="express"/><ref name="xfactor2">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2449042/Prison-officer-Sam-Screwbo-Bailey-leads-pampered-parade-X-Factor-finalists-superstar-makeovers.html|title=What a transformation! Prison officer Sam 'Screwbo' Bailey leads the pampered parade as the X Factor finalists get superstar makeovers|date=7 October 2013|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|publisher=[[DMG_Media|DMG Media]]|accessdate=8 October 2013}}</ref><ref name="express">{{cite web|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/448303/X-Factor-finalist-Sam-Bailey-heads-home-to-Leicester-to-greet-her-husband-and-children|title=X Factor finalist Sam Bailey heads home to Leicester to greet her husband and children|date=12 December 2013|last=McCormack|first=Kirsty|work=[[Daily_Express|Daily Express]]|accessdate=15 December 2013}}</ref> 貝莉與皮爾森相遇於2002年，並於2003年1月29日在[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]結婚。<ref name="Jackie Bailey"/>

